thread.title_full: Redspot Car Rentals reviewed by GARY

author: GARY
title: GARY
text: I have used Redspot on two occasions over the last several months. One for a family holiday the other was for a business trip. From booking to collection of vehicle and return, was seamless. Staff on both occasions were very professional, helpful and courteous. Price was very competitive with bigger named companies.Will definitely use Redspot again.
